{"id":161597,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/德国之声-美大使在联合国人权理事会批评中国人/","date":"2011-06-16T04:30:17Z","modified":"2011-06-16T04:30:17Z","title":"德国之声 | 美大使在联合国人权理事会批评中国人权状况","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国代表在联合国人权理事会上呼吁，</span>14<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">个人权状况很差的国家应该在人权的问题上担负责任。美国大使多纳霍在发言中表示：</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">太多的国家压制异见，却不会因此受到惩罚。</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国代表提交的这份</span>“<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">非法治国家</span>”<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">名单中包括中国、伊朗、利比亚、朝鲜、白俄罗斯、古巴、巴林、缅甸、斯里兰卡、苏丹、叙利亚、委内瑞拉、也门和津巴布韦。多纳霍批评中国越来越多地逮捕律师、人权活动者、博客作家、艺术家和宗教教徒。她还对伊朗发生的政治谋杀以及缅甸大规模逮捕反对派人士予以指责。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15157047%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%BC%9A%E6%89%B9%E8%AF%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%9D%83%E7%8A%B6%E5%86%B5\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"